The PEATSA module contains tools for calculating a the effect of mutations on a number of properties of a protein.

The Core sub-module contains the ProteinDesignTool command line program along with the classes that make it tick.
See INSTALL in Core for whats required to install this tool.

The WebApp sub-module defines a LAMP (linux apache mysql php) Web Application that is built on top of the core ProteinDesignTool.
It utilises some of the classes defined in the Core module.
See INSTALL in WebApp for information on how to set up this web application.
